import React from 'react'
import Navbar from './components/Navbar/Navbar'
import './App.css'
import Home from './components/pages/Home'
import {BrowserRouter as Router, Route } from 'react-router-dom'

function App() {
  return (
    <>
        <Navbar />
          <Route path="/" exact component={Home} />
    </>
  )
}

export default App
